sequenceDiagram
    participant Plugin as 浏览器插件
    participant API as FastAPI / IntakeService
    participant Hermes as HermesOrchestrator
    participant PW as PlaywrightWorker
    participant Evidence as EvidenceService
    participant Draft as DocumentDraftService
    participant LLM as MiMo LLM
    participant Notify as NotificationAdapter

    Plugin->>API: 提交 URL / 标题 / HTML / 截图 / 正文
    API->>Hermes: submit_capture_workflow(case_id)
    API->>PW: 缺失截图或 HTML 时补抓
    API->>Evidence: 生成证据包并落盘

    Note over Hermes,Draft: 监控链路命中后，也会复用 Hermes
    Hermes->>LLM: generate_case_summary(case_context, evidence_context)
    Hermes->>Notify: 触发风险通知

    Draft->>Hermes: submit_document_workflow(template_key, case_id)
    Hermes->>LLM: generate_document_draft(template, case, evidence)
    LLM-->>Draft: 返回可审核 Markdown 草稿

